Class SVOElement

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.articulate.sigma.nlg.SVOElement

  • public class SVOElement
extends java.lang.Object
    An element in a sentence conceived of as having a Subject-Verb-Object grammar. Not all properties will be used by all the positions.
